   <p><a name="index-reftex_002dinsert_002dlabel_002dflags-142"></a><a name="index-reftex_002dlabel_002dmenu_002dflags-143"></a>Depending on how you would like the label insertion and selection for
the new environments to work, you might want to add the letters `<samp><span class="samp">a</span></samp>'
and `<samp><span class="samp">h</span></samp>' to some of the flags in the variables
<code>reftex-insert-label-flags</code> (see <a href="#Options-_002d-Creating-Labels">Options - Creating Labels</a>)
and <code>reftex-label-menu-flags</code> (see <a href="#Options-_002d-Referencing-Labels">Options - Referencing Labels</a>).

