<h2 class="chapter">7 RefTeX's Menu</h2>

<p><a name="index-RefTeXs-Menu-287"></a><a name="index-Menu_002c-in-the-menu-bar-288"></a>
RefTeX installs a <code>Ref</code> menu in the menu bar on systems
which support this.  From this menu you can access all of
RefTeX's commands and a few of its options.  There is also a
<code>Customize</code> submenu which can be used to access RefTeX's
entire set of options.

