<h2 class="chapter">18 Options, Keymaps, Hooks</h2>

<p><a name="index-Options_002c-list-of-439"></a>
Here is a complete list of RefTeX's configuration variables.  All
variables have customize support, so if you are not familiar with Emacs
Lisp (and even if you are) you might find it more comfortable to use
<code>customize</code> to look at and change these variables. <kbd>M-x
reftex-customize</kbd> will get you there.

   <p>In case you don't use the <code>customize</code> interface, here's a caveat:
Changing (mostly parsing-related) options might require a call to
<code>reftex-compile-variables</code> in order to become effective.

